{"tid":1167347,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"玩股票有兩種人，往往第二種死得最快","createTime":"2019-05-23T03:42:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T04:12:13.000Z","uid":224632,"like":21,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3269306728bfa75a253c7efed49da9266a089b47","tid":1167347,"uid":224632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:42:06.000Z","msg":"第一種就係玩股票追漲殺跌，人云亦云。<br />\n<br />\n往往係大市升既時候就追，，一開始就會有啲甜頭，但之後面對住既係突然既急跌，而啲股倉從始被蟹。<br />\n<br />\n抱住終有一日都會升番上去既心態，收吓息，短期係好傷，但係正股驚西！長期黎講都偶有小賺。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二種就唔再係人云亦云啦，而係人云乜佢就云對家&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;姐係死都唔信邪。<br />\n<br />\n呢種通常都好聰明，日日追住幅圖，睇新聞，再用自己驚世既頭腦去玩股票，簡直上知天文下知地理，政治角力乜乜柒柒都預測到。股票既波動已經滿足唔到佢地，所以就會玩衍生產品（大部份都牛熊，玩期權哥啲唔包括，因為已經超越咗呢種人）都未夠，一定要借埋錢！<br />\n<br />\n風險？唔洗控制啦，覺得升就會升，覺得跌就會跌，全倉！最後輸晒啲錢抱撚住個頭係到諗點算時，先發現原來自己係好聰明，不過係自作聰明嗰種聰明。<br />\n<br />\n利申：點算？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d892b29c539df650d0d9e30d2dcc379465ab31e","tid":1167347,"uid":195515,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:43:25.000Z","msg":"再借 下一次就係機會"},{"pid":"75f3ecaf2f3405f92aa491fec4cf1e975e319ad1","tid":1167347,"uid":254259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:44:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d775b8f9e671db1368b8e63bcd3fb4ab469173eb","tid":1167347,"uid":110988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi